**/SMPLX_*.npz
**/SMPLH_*.npz
**/SMPLH_*.pkl
**/SMPL_*.pkl
**/SMPLX_*.pkl

# Motion datasets: ignore bulk downloads; curated demo clips are tracked.
# (holosoma, parc_ms, GLB are not listed here — they commit as-is.)
