# AMASS: track all curated demos under mimic/; bulk AMASS elsewhere stays ignored
assets/motions/mimic/AMASS/*
!assets/motions/mimic/AMASS/
!assets/motions/mimic/AMASS/**
assets/motions/intermimic/OMOMO/*
!assets/motions/intermimic/OMOMO/sub10_largebox_000/
!assets/motions/intermimic/OMOMO/sub10_largebox_000/**
!assets/motions/intermimic/OMOMO/sub12_woodchair_000/
!assets/motions/intermimic/OMOMO/sub12_woodchair_000/**
